"review_level": "None",
"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:10.6.1.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">10.6.1.1</span> 標題：沒藥（myrrh）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： לֹט</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： lot)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:25\">GEN 37:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:11\">GEN 43:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מֹר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mor)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:23\">EXO 30:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:12\">EST 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:9\">PSA 45:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:17\">PRO 7:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:13\">SNG 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song3:6\">SNG 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:6\">SNG 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song4:14\">SNG 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:1\">SNG 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:5\">SNG 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:5\">SNG 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:13\">SNG 5:13</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： μυροβρεχής</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： murobrechēs)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc4:6\">3MA 4:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： μύρον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： muron)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:7\">MAT 26:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:12\">MAT 26:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:3\">MRK 14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:4\">MRK 14:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:38\">LUK 7:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:46\">LUK 7:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:2\">JHN 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:3\">JHN 12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:3\">JHN 12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:5\">JHN 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:13\">REV 18:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt10:3\">JDT 10:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis2:7\">WIS 2:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： σμύρνα, σμυρνίζω</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： smurna, smurnizō（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:11\">MAT 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:23\">MRK 15:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir24:15\">SIR 24:15</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>沒藥是某些灌木的芳香樹脂。這種樹脂可以加到油基中，製成香水塗在身上。另參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">4.8.3.1 防腐油、香膏 (embalming oils)&lt;REALIA:4.8.3.1&gt;</a> 。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>以色列當地沒有出產沒藥樹脂的樹木，沒藥需要進口，因此非常昂貴。翻譯者在翻譯<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:12\">EST 2:12</a> 、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:9\">PSA 45:9</a> （《和》45:8）、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:17\">PRO 7:17</a> 、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:13\">SNG 1:13</a> 、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:11\">MAT 2:11</a> 時，應該記住這一點。</p>\n<p>大多數翻譯者借用一個術語來翻譯「沒藥」。在一些經文中，翻譯者可能會展開譯文，來說明這種物質的性質；比較<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:9\">PSA 45:9</a> （《和》45:8）中的譯文“perfume of myrrh”「沒藥做的香水」。在許多情況下，尤其是在《新約》，翻譯者可能會採用一般性的表達，比如「油膏」、「芳香的油」或「香水」。當希臘文<em>muron</em> 指「香水」時，可以譯為「散發香味的油」或「芳香的油」。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
